               <msContents>
                  <summary>Praises of Mary, ውዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡; Gate of Light, አንቀጸ፡ ብርሃን፡; Angels Praise Her, ይዌድስዋ፡ መላእክት፡ ለማርያም፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="34v"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2509Weddas"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="35r" to="50v"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1113Anqasa"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="50v" to="55r"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT3108RepCh388"/>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
